{"tid":1722484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[票債不能血償]Sorry有人唔係淨係想要區選","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:18:45.000Z","uid":7270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d863616925f494e25ad69c56d339bbee3cb2c7a7","tid":1722484,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:00:48.000Z","msg":"中大既手足，首先多謝你地咁辛苦，守左咁多日。<br />\n但我覺得你地個叫價太低，只係要求區選順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n其實港共一早吹緊風叫人投票，佢恨不得可以用區選維穩。係無政制改變底下，區選變相係反映唔到民意，亦唔見得需要用咁多人死傷去換返來。<br />\n<br />\n但連登一定有人屌我分化撚，因為區選係神聖而不可侵犯的。<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好岩岩打返起個勢又諗住血債票償好無？<br />\n唉。<br />\n<br />\n有人係想要真真正正既普選，但呢個po俾人拉沉我預左的了。"},{"pid":"5e6554df44302cc8bfe3d087463545c6893fa7af","tid":1722484,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"Topic打錯，係血債不能票償"},{"pid":"842598706bce6f7e2f57fe7050c17197befe73ee","tid":1722484,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:01:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d975cb9c714e915679d9102021791e92ae4e6151","tid":1722484,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e6554df44302cc8bfe3d087463545c6893fa7af","tid":1722484,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"Topic打錯，係血債不能票償"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"我再開過先"},{"pid":"531fe396132e3bf4e42b8b155d54645113d7dfd2","tid":1722484,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"關於被自殺，大家有無發現有共通點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722333</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"133071de2bd0984e254e3c000416da24a0cecdbb","tid":1722484,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"區選成績 半數議席都贏唔到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724079</a>"}]}